{"type":"assistant.message","data":{"messageId":"8ae52279-1877-496f-b957-97bf7225312f","content":"No repo-specific guidance found, so here's the general migration path:\n\n## Migrating from VSTest@3 → Microsoft.Testing.Platform\n\n### 1. Update your test projects\n\nIn each `.csproj`, enable the new platform and add the TRX/coverage packages:\n\n```xml\n<PropertyGroup>\n  <EnableMSTestRunner>true</EnableMSTestRunner>\n  <TestingPlatformDotnetTestSupport>true</TestingPlatformDotnetTestSupport>\n</PropertyGroup>\n\n<ItemGroup>\n  <PackageReference Include=\"Microsoft.Testing.Extensions.TrxReport\" Version=\"1.*\" />\n  <PackageReference Include=\"Microsoft.Testing.Extensions.CodeCoverage\" Version=\"17.*\" />\n</ItemGroup>\n```\n\n### 2. Replace VSTest@3 with DotNetCoreCLI@2\n\n```yaml\n# Before\n- task: VSTest@3\n  inputs:\n    testSelector: 'testAssemblies'\n    testAssemblyVer2: '**\\*Tests.dll'\n    resultsFolder: $(Agent.TempDirectory)\\TestResults\n\n# After\n- task: DotNetCoreCLI@2\n  displayName: 'Run tests'\n  inputs:\n    command: test\n    projects: '**/*Tests.csproj'\n    arguments: >-\n      --no-build\n      --results-directory $(Agent.TempDirectory)/TestResults\n      -- --report-trx\n         --coverage\n         --coverage-output-format cobertura\n```\n\n### 3. Publish results & coverage\n\n```yaml\n- task: PublishTestResults@2\n  condition: always()\n  inputs:\n    testResultsFormat: VSTest\n    testResultsFiles: '**/*.trx'\n    searchFolder: $(Agent.TempDirectory)/TestResults\n\n- task: PublishCodeCoverageResults@2\n  condition: always()\n  inputs:\n    summaryFileLocation: '$(Agent.TempDirectory)/TestResults/**/*.cobertura.xml'\n```\n\n**Key points:**\n- `EnableMSTestRunner` makes each test project a standalone executable.\n- `TestingPlatformDotnetTestSupport` keeps `dotnet test` working as the entry point.\n- `--report-trx` and `--coverage` are passed after `--` (platform-level args).\n- Use `condition: always()` so results publish even on test failure.","toolRequests":[],"interactionId":"f5336492-e616-4e14-8498-eaf18c4f316e","outputTokens":583,"requestId":"0437:CA693:1E58809:22294C7:69E81A23"},"id":"c3cd9324-e652-4379-a96c-b5649b1efadc","timestamp":"2026-04-22T00:45:34.976Z","parentId":"6af4c8a4-3c27-444c-8957-14894879ad50"}
